description:
Microsoft Team Foundation Server Extended Client

Integrate with Microsoft Team Foundation Server and Visual Studio Team Services from desktop-based Windows applications.  Work with and manage version control, work items, and build, and other resources from your client application.
releaseNotes: Version 14.83.1, fixes an issue where the import entry for the included targets file is not automatically added to the visual studio project file.  This target import ensures the native binaries get copied to the output directory at build time.
title: Microsoft Team Foundation Server Extended Client
